<h2 data-section-id="9aynlo" data-start="23" data-end="74"><span role="text">💡 Agar oldin <code data-start="40" data-end="57">createsuperuser</code> qilgan bo‘lsang:</span></h2>
<p data-start="76" data-end="170">👉 Yangi user yaratganingda <strong data-start="104" data-end="133">eski user o‘chib ketmaydi</strong><br data-start="133" data-end="136">
👉 Ikkalasi ham database’da qoladi</p>
<hr data-start="172" data-end="175">
<h2 data-section-id="m9plji" data-start="177" data-end="191">🔍 Qisqasi:</h2>
<ul data-start="192" data-end="273">
<li data-section-id="1xnjjbu" data-start="192" data-end="217">
<p data-start="194" data-end="217">Eski admin → qoladi ✅</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1jhogyk" data-start="218" data-end="248">
<p data-start="220" data-end="248">Yangi admin → qo‘shiladi ✅</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1oksde1" data-start="249" data-end="273">
<p data-start="251" data-end="273">Hech narsa o‘chmaydi ❌</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="275" data-end="278">
<h2 data-section-id="1sg5nd5" data-start="280" data-end="308">🤔 Qachon muammo bo‘ladi?</h2>
<p data-start="310" data-end="330">Faqat bitta holatda:</p>
<h3 data-section-id="6e764o" data-start="332" data-end="361">❗ Username bir xil bo‘lsa</h3>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="362" data-end="397"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-df3050c8.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Bash</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Копировать" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-df3050c8.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="relative"><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>Username already exists</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="399" data-end="454">👉 Unda boshqa nom yozasan (masalan: <code data-start="436" data-end="444">admin2</code>, <code data-start="446" data-end="453">user1</code>)</p>
<hr data-start="456" data-end="459">
<h2 data-section-id="1rflaox" data-start="461" data-end="505">🧹 Agar eski userni o‘chirmoqchi bo‘lsang</h2>
<p data-start="507" data-end="527">Admin panelga kirib:</p>
<ul data-start="528" data-end="578">
<li data-section-id="1x2y7i3" data-start="528" data-end="549">
<p data-start="530" data-end="549">Users bo‘limiga o‘t</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1d1cced" data-start="550" data-end="578">
<p data-start="552" data-end="578">Keraksiz userni delete qil</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="580" data-end="583">
<h2 data-section-id="1kzncmq" data-start="585" data-end="599">🔥 Maslahat</h2>
<p data-start="600" data-end="725">Agar parolni unutgan bo‘lsang, yangi user ochish osonroq 😄<br data-start="659" data-end="662">
yoki men senga <strong data-start="677" data-end="725">parolni reset qilishni ham ko‘rsatib beraman</strong></p>
<hr data-start="727" data-end="730">
